article.linkText: Calvin scores 21, Wright State beats Northern Kentucky 85-78
article.story: HIGHLAND HEIGHTS, Ky. -- — Trey Calvin's 21 points helped Wright State defeat Northern Kentucky 85-78 on Sunday. Calvin also contributed six rebounds for the Raiders (13-11, 8-5 Horizon League). Alex Huibregste added 17 points and 10 assists. Brandon Noel scored 15 on 6-for-9 shooting. The Norse (11-12, 6-6) were led in scoring by Marques Warrick with 20 points. Michael Bradley totaled 17 points and four assists. Trey Robinson pitched in with 15 points, nine rebounds and four steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
